Text:
Thanks alot for the FCUP ul, Ichthypod_Crane!  It's a mighty impressive torrent and nearly everything that FC published.  (Too bad about those missing issues - maybe someday someone will fill those).

About the missing Eclipse titles, that many titles and issues missing is rather disturbing.  I'm guessing you'll have about 70-80% of Eclipse to ul!  It'll be interesting to see what's coming.

Are you calling this ECUP?  ;-)
Man, thank you for uploading all your First torrents, and congratulations on finishing it. What an awesome collection of a sorely missed publisher's titles. Thanks again!
I haven't read that Mazinger book in quite a while but I remember it having great art. Thanks.
